            <lb/>Et <persName><forename>Jehan</forename><surname>ledoulx</surname></persName> bourgeois <expan>et</expan> marchant de <expan><placeName>bourdeaus</placeName></expan> inthime Et
            <lb/><expan>autrement</expan><expan>demandeur</expan><expan><choice><orig>linterinement</orig><reg>l’interinement</reg></choice></expan> de <expan>ladite</expan><expan>requeste</expan><expan><choice><orig>dautre</orig><reg>d’autre</reg></choice></expan></ab><ab><lb/>Veu par la <expan>court</expan> le proces <expan>Enqueste</expan><expan>faite</expan> par <expan>ledit</expan> appellant
            <lb/>a <placeName>marmande</placeName> le <choice><orig>dixneufuieme</orig><reg>dixneufvieme</reg></choice><choice><orig>apuril</orig><reg>apvril</reg></choice> mil VC cinquante neuf
            <lb/><expan>Requeste</expan><expan>presentee</expan> a <expan>ladite</expan><expan>court</expan> par <expan>ledit</expan> inthime le <expan>septieme</expan> jung mil VC
            <lb/>soixante troys tendent aux fins <expan>qu’il</expan> luy pleut en jugeant
            <lb/><expan>ledit</expan> appel juger le principal de la matiere <expan>Appoinctement</expan><lb/>a corriger tant sur <expan>ledit</expan> appel que sur <expan>ladite</expan><expan>requeste</expan> du
            <lb/><subst><del><expan>quatorzieme</expan> decembre</del><add hand="#MainFDLG" place="top">neufiesme daoust</add></subst> mil VC soixante troys Corrige des <expan>parties</expan><lb/>Et leurs <expan>autres</expan> pieces et production <expan>faite</expan> en <expan>ladite</expan> court
          </ab><ab><lb/>Il sera dit Que la court mect <choice><orig>lappel</orig><reg>l’appel</reg></choice><expan>et</expan> ce dont a este
            <lb/>appelle au neant Et ordonne que <expan>ledit</expan><persName>sacriste</persName> payera
            <lb/><expan>audit</expan><persName>ledoulx</persName> les despens des <expan>comminations</expan> mentionnees en
            <lb/>la sentence <expan>dudit</expan> seneschal Et le <expan>procureur</expan><expan>dudit</expan><persName>sacriste</persName><lb/>vingt solz tournois <expan>pour</expan><choice><orig>nauoir</orig><reg>n’avoir</reg></choice><expan>conclud</expan> Et en interinant <expan>ladite</expan><lb/><expan>requeste</expan><expan>dudit</expan><expan>septieme</expan> jun mil VC soixante trois retient la
            <lb/>cognoissance du principal de la <expan>matiere</expan> Et faisant droict
            <lb/><choice><orig>dicelluy</orig><reg>d’icelluy</reg></choice> ordonne que la sentence du juge ordinaire sortira
            <lb/>son plain <expan>et</expan> entier effect Condempne <expan>ledit</expan><persName>sacriste</persName><choice><orig>enuers</orig><reg>envers</reg></choice><lb/><expan>ledit</expan><persName>ledoulx</persName> ez despens faictz tant <expan>pardevant</expan><expan>ledit</expan> juge
            <lb/><expan>ordinaire</expan> seneschal que en la court La taxe <choice><orig>diceulx</orig><reg>d’iceulx</reg></choice><lb/>a elle <choice><orig>Reseruee</orig><reg>Reservee</reg></choice></ab><ab rend="left" type="signature"><handShift new="#MainFDLG"/><lb/><persName>f de guyonye</persName></ab><ab rend="center"><lb/><foreign xml:lang="lat"><expan>habeat</expan><expan>Relator</expan></foreign> quatre escus
          </ab><ab corresp="#MainMDM" rend="left" type="signature"><handShift new="#MainMDM"/><lb/><persName><forename>michel</forename><nameLink>de</nameLink><surname><choice><orig>mōtaigne</orig><reg>montaigne</reg></choice></surname></persName><foreign xml:lang="lat">relator</foreign></ab><ab corresp="#MainMDM" rend="right"><lb/><sic>Messieur</sic><list><item><choice><orig>presidāt</orig><reg>presidant</reg></choice><persName>la guionie</persName></item><item><persName>eimar</persName></item><item><persName>fayard</persName></item><item><persName>massei</persName></item><item><persName>de alis</persName></item><item><persName>beringuier</persName></item><item><persName>du plessi</persName></item><item><persName>rignac</persName></item><item><persName>macanan</persName></item><item><persName><choice><orig>mōtaigne</orig><reg>montaigne</reg></choice></persName> raporteur</item></list></ab><ab rend="center"><handShift new="#MainX2"/><lb/><date when="1564-03-16">XVIe mars VCLXIII</date></ab></div></body></text></TEI>